{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"37276-a-day-at-the-carnival","title":"A Day at the Carnival","description":"The three mice brothers can’t wait to visit the carnival. They ride toy cars, go on the Ferris wheel, and visit the balloon shop. After some time, they realize their youngest brother is missing! Where can he be?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Alisha Berger"],"illustrators":["Nivong  Sengsakoun"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/37276-a-day-at-the-carnival"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93876/size3/a434ae08226f7e4fb4da5b52fb4e12b5.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93876/size6/a434ae08226f7e4fb4da5b52fb4e12b5.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71011/size6/f6ddeaa4fe3850a7cfd3dccd7f152bbc.jpg","text":"It's carnival day.\nHooray! \nshouts Little Mouse.\nHooray! \nshouts Littler Mouse.\nHooray! \nshouts Tiny Mouse.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71012/size6/3be2c0c685291db3c93fe8d13aade8f4.jpg","text":"They plan to ride every ride!\n“But don't lose me!”\nTiny Mouse tells his brothers.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79594/size6/0ebb798d8220a7e7bd0fc4d675c1319d.jpg","text":"They race each other on toy cars.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71015/size6/8c4137a542c17ebc759e42a16a66acbd.jpg","text":"They go up and down on the merry-go-round.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71017/size6/32f85a5b3a561f401fb7fa691725a09f.jpg","text":"They ride the winding caterpillar coaster.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71020/size6/a0ca13b48f635e92aa6c620051a42e65.jpg","text":"They take a spin on the Ferris wheel.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71021/size6/a63f846ca90ecfb52e567de8fc566f04.jpg","text":"The brothers walk to the balloon cart...","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71023/size6/b8acc946b2e20dd1e50ca5cd2bccadfd.jpg","text":"...and they each \nbuy a balloon.\n \nOne balloon, two balloons...","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71025/size6/0ad4427a7e783c5dfd25b53706535c6b.jpg","text":"“Wait, where is Tiny Mouse?”","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71027/size6/545eb4ea55d62a5db0f59845669b9eb8.jpg","text":"Little Mouse and Littler Mouse run to the toy cars. \nTiny Mouse isn't there.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71028/size6/e6182dbf1fe1f7d9a5df5f9b7aa5f56b.jpg","text":"They run to the merry-go-round. \nTiny Mouse isn't there.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71030/size6/3f100cc99d23cd57bd553ba32bd0200e.jpg","text":"They run to the caterpillar coaster. \nTiny Mouse isn't there, either.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71032/size6/a7caeadaa88e9313a20408c7b3b98765.jpg","text":"They run to the Ferris wheel. \nThank goodness!\nThere is Tiny Mouse!","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71033/size6/2d13ecc12098d68365a1362816ff0323.jpg","text":"The Little Mice each buy a glass of sugarcane juice.\nOne glass, two glasses, three glasses!","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71035/size6/f67ad9252d90732f811c77a6ebea1739.jpg","text":"What a fantastic day at the carnival.\nHooray, Hooray, Hooray!","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71037/size6/0eab2acd245ef0a2da9f7268920c492e.jpg","text":"17/17","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":154}}